t":"鲁迅的论述找一下。文史哲两篇是否发，想一下。清华北大不要写大文章，就某一个问题写。力求改进文风，短的，短文，行就用，不行就下期，这期要有文章。主席指示传开之后，开座谈会之类，过几天。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"7752af50e2","type":"paragraph","text":"主席对出《水浒》，不满意71回本，把投降的东西掩盖了，金圣叹砍的。百回本除线装之外未出。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"16f9e03c04","type":"paragraph","text":"主席指示传达后，出版局震动，要他们从积极方面领会。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"acfb1c675d","type":"paragraph","text":"宋江搞修正主义过去没有提过。宋江摒晁盖于108人之外，所有文章都未提到过。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"deb1f36f84","type":"paragraph","text":"主席文章是经过深思熟虑的，亲自改的（批示）。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"154d37fcc8","type":"paragraph","text":"主席指示上海明天可以收到，联系一下，看看写什么文章，有什么反映。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"95456b4cfb","type":"paragraph","text":"你们要办的几项：","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"3d22f7db2f","type":"paragraph","text":"① 鲁迅论《水浒》有无其他的段落，","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"80b20642a5","type":"paragraph","text":"② 南开一篇，改改最好，","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"afc0e04c79","type":"paragraph","text":"③ 《文史哲》两篇不能发，要请示，","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"0db3cd2b42","type":"paragraph","text":"④ 清华北大，写短的，","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"6ec9d707a2","type":"paragraph","text":"⑤ 鲁迅一段之后，写一短文。","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"e94e1ad199","type":"paragraph","text":"主席关心资产阶级法权问题。红线女写一封信，说在乡下看了，盐的价格山区比城市贵得多，太原每斤0.11元，平顺0.13元，西沟0.18元。价值规律应为无产阶级政治服务，不应扩大差别。主席认为要注意，要关心，要议一下。我们一期思想动态也反映，山区利息高，不愿要贷款。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"c036e36e9b","type":"paragraph","text":"资产阶级法权问题要研究。","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"c12297cd34","type":"paragraph","text":"存稿，很难考虑用那些，今年定不再发的，撤掉。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"143f8fcab8","type":"paragraph","text":"王莽一篇可留，","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"ec4254daf9","type":"paragraph","text":"经济主义一篇可留，","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"dfdc3b8653","type":"paragraph","text":"基本路线一篇可留，","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"f4602c521d","type":"paragraph","text":"襄樊棉纺厂一篇改写，从领导角度讲，","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"ea72382d79","type":"paragraph","text":"其余可撤版。","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"91351d270c","type":"paragraph","text":"关羽一篇可以发，待适当时机。主席讲过，孔子批了，武圣也可以批了。这篇要发的。现集中批宋江。过去一般讲法，《水浒》前段好的，现在看前段也不行了，把晁盖搞掉了，最早是晁盖搞起来的，鲁迅评论，终于是奴才。","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"9cd6d0bdac","type":"paragraph","text":"一个《水浒后传》，三阮找吴用。","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"719a2d9a5b","type":"paragraph","text":"李希凡竭力为宋江辩护，全传序是他写的，反驳对宋江的批判，这当然是思想问题。","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"ef015b3466","type":"paragraph","text":"五七干校（的报告）批了，能办吧？合理也合法。","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"272125687f","type":"paragraph","text":"下期纸头要多一点，可以的，最后用那些稿件今天不定。","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"53dcf6ba21","type":"paragraph","text":"码头文章，组成一组可以。","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"e022318dde","type":"paragraph","text":"卫生文章可以。体育一篇可和卫生合一起。","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"380a95d6ef","type":"paragraph","text":"文化战线评《水浒》的文章带头。","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"18beac9781","type":"paragraph","text":"学理论第二组。上期学习一组有什么反映？","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"242184b647","type":"paragraph","text":"金山，基建文章。","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"114d5d482e","type":"paragraph","text":"要用的稿子重送一次，","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"98f8ca5128","type":"paragraph","text":"鲁迅诗一篇，看看再说。","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"3298dc11e2","type":"paragraph","text":"鲁迅轶文，由人民日报发，我们不一定评论。","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"5ff39c1ae5","type":"paragraph","text":"这期集中评《水浒》。座谈会暂时不开。","index":41,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"094761c90f","type":"paragraph","text":"原考虑农业、价格都拟开（座谈会）","index":42,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"56822b11e2","type":"paragraph","text":"十大关系，重新整理，主席看过，本来建议发表，主席说仍（等）选集出了再发。毛选五卷正在编，已定稿一批，出五卷是大事，有一半是发表过的，要组织好多文章宣传，看看国庆时如何。","index":43,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"a2fd608868","type":"paragraph","text":"河南大水灾，有的说是千年不遇大水灾。国务院正在全力抢救。","index":44,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"4116f0260b","type":"paragraph","text":"对不正当协作有这样反映：“这样做是不对的，不干是不行的，干起来是有效的，以后还是要检讨的。”天津讲协作的文章可以改一改。听听计委的意见。","index":45,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"7ba415712a","type":"paragraph","text":"技术革命提倡不够。今年钢死命抓，（达到）2600万吨仍危险。","index":46,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"d6ac982ba3","type":"paragraph","text":"（调查）轮流下去，下次到东北。","index":47,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"78cf1a9bf4","type":"paragraph","text":"国庆节，讲成就、路线，有的预先作考虑，有计划安排，综合的，先进的，个人、集体，预作准备。","index":48,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"1fc542c563","type":"paragraph","text":"准备一篇讲抗灾的斗争，坏事，奋斗后，变好了，锻炼党、军队、人民以及政治、经济工作。这次集中一年雨量，京广路仍未通，皖、鄂也紧张，积水，要在安徽炸堤坝，安徽要牺牲，做工作。","index":49,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"},{"id":"83e7781606","type":"paragraph","text":"现要排水，通车，才好救灾。","index":50,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901"}],"page":{"id":"f8c23a54fe","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"65a453e901","start":0,"end":0}},"yaowe